{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01FN2ve4iPhn38o4kjv7fuoH","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Quarkus-Specific Annotations Analysis:\n- CDI Annotations:\n  - @ApplicationScoped: Used in services and repositories\n  - @Inject: Dependency injection\n  - @RequestScoped: Web request lifecycle\n  - @Named: CDI bean naming\n\n- JAX-RS Annotations:\n  - @Path: REST endpoint paths\n  - @GET, @POST: HTTP method definitions\n  - @Produces: Response content type\n  - @QueryParam, @FormParam: Parameter bindings\n\n- JPA/Hibernate Annotations:\n  - @Entity: JPA entities\n  - @Table: Database table mapping\n  - @Id: Primary key\n  - @Column: Column mappings\n  - @OneToMany, @ManyToOne: Relationship mappings\n  - @Transactional: Transaction management\n\n- Other Annotations:\n  - @Observes: CDI event observation\n  - @Temporal: Date/time mapping\n  - @NamedQueries: Predefined database queries\n\nDetailed Project Components:\n1. Entities:\n- CustomerOrder\n- LineItem\n- Part\n- Vendor\n- VendorPart\n\n2. Repositories:\n- CustomerOrderRepository\n- LineItemRepository\n- PartRepository\n- VendorRepository\n- VendorPartRepository\n\n3. Web Controllers:\n- OrderWebController (HTML-based interactions)\n- OrderController (Additional controller)\n\n4. Services:\n- OrderConfigService\n\nKey Observations:\n- Uses H2 in-memory database\n- Implements a complex order management system\n- Leverages Quarkus for dependency injection, ORM, and web routing\n- Uses Qute for HTML templating\n- Supports CRUD operations on various entities\n- Implements complex database relationships\n\nWould you like me to dive deeper into any specific aspect of this Quarkus application?"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3bf9647-5068-4947-ac84-3cc2f665ec1a","uuid":"5098e152-ac26-4077-a3b7-6cdfcef28ae1"}
