{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Gdg4z1zNVDLEhGoWTys3CV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I need to refactor the Java source code. The key changes needed:\n1. Change package names from `quarkus.tutorial.order` to `jakarta.tutorial.order`\n2. Replace `io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent` with a Jakarta EE `@Singleton @Startup` EJB\n3. Replace `io.quarkus.qute.Template`/`TemplateInstance` with Servlet-based JSP forwarding\n4. Replace `@PersistenceContext` usage (already correct for JakartaEE)\n5. The entities already use `jakarta.persistence.*` imports - good!\n6. CDI annotations already use `jakarta.enterprise.*` and `jakarta.inject.*` - good!\n7. JAX-RS annotations already use `jakarta.ws.rs.*` - good!\n\nThe main Quarkus-specific code is:\n- `OrderWebController.java` - uses Qute `Template` and `TemplateInstance`\n- `StartupInitializer.java` - uses `io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent`\n\nLet me create the new package directory structure and refactored files. I'll move the source files to the new package and rewrite the Quarkus-specific ones."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":444,"cache_read_input_tokens":65208,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":444,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":475},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3bf9647-5068-4947-ac84-3cc2f665ec1a","uuid":"40a251cf-8771-40c5-a032-6da3a9c029c7"}
