{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NSfhhK2RrZWXnFEjiRDZzV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks completed. Here is the migration report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks involved:** Quarkus 3.30.5 -> Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty)\n- **High-level actions performed:**\n  1. Analyzed 16 Java source files across entity, repository, service, and web layers\n  2. Replaced Quarkus BOM and all `io.quarkus` dependencies with `jakarta.jakartaee-api:10.0.0`\n  3. Migrated package names from `quarkus.tutorial.order` to `jakarta.tutorial.order`\n  4. Replaced Quarkus Qute templating with JAX-RS HTML string builders\n  5. Replaced Quarkus `@Observes StartupEvent` with Jakarta EE `@Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct`\n  6. Created Open Liberty server.xml, JPA persistence.xml, web.xml, and beans.xml\n  7. Updated Dockerfile to multi-stage build with Open Liberty runtime\n  8. Generated 6 smoke tests covering all major endpoints\n- **Overall outcome:** SUCCESS - All 6 smoke tests pass, application fully functional\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus dependencies with Jakarta EE 10 + Open Liberty\n- Dockerfile: Multi-stage build with Maven builder and Open Liberty runtime\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty server config (webProfile-10.0, H2 datasource)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit configuration\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Jakarta EE web application descriptor\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI 4.0 configuration\n- src/main/webapp/index.html: Redirect page to /orders\n- src/main/webapp/css/default.css: Stylesheet (copied from resources)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/entity/*.java: 7 entity classes (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/repository/*.java: 5 repository classes (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/service/OrderConfigService.java: Data init service (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderController.java: Business controller (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderWebController.java: REST controller (Qute -> HTML builders)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/StartupInitializer.java: Startup EJB (StartupEvent -> @Singleton @Startup)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/JakartaRestApplication.java: JAX-RS application class\n- smoke.py: 6 HTTP smoke tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/: Entire old package directory\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Quarkus-specific configuration\n- src/main/resources/templates/: Qute templates (orders.html, orderTemplate.html, lineItems.html, lineItemTemplate.html)\n- src/main/resources/css/: CSS (moved to webapp)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T03:30:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - 16 Java files, Quarkus 3.30.5\n[2026-03-17T03:31:00Z] [info] Generated smoke.py with 6 test cases\n[2026-03-17T03:32:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml - replaced all Quarkus deps with Jakarta EE 10\n[2026-03-17T03:33:00Z] [info] Created server.xml, persistence.xml, web.xml, beans.xml\n[2026-03-17T03:34:00Z] [info] Migrated all Java packages quarkus.tutorial -> jakarta.tutorial\n[2026-03-17T03:36:00Z] [info] Replaced Quarkus StartupEvent with @Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct\n[2026-03-17T03:36:30Z] [info] Replaced Qute templates with HTML string builders\n[2026-03-17T03:38:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile - multi-stage build with Open Liberty\n[2026-03-17T03:39:00Z] [error] Build fail: apt-get not found on UBI image - fixed to dnf\n[2026-03-17T03:40:00Z] [error] H2 URL format error + ORB error - fixed server.xml config\n[2026-03-17T03:41:00Z] [info] Successful build and deployment - Liberty started in 3.9s\n[2026-03-17T03:42:00Z] [info] All 6 smoke tests passed (0 failures)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 2 errors encountered and resolved during Docker build/deploy\n- **Critical Issues:** None remaining - all resolved\n- **Error 1 (severity: warning):** UBI image uses `dnf` not `apt-get` - resolved by switching package manager\n- **Error 2 (severity: error):** H2 datasource URL parsing error due to incorrect Liberty server.xml config - resolved by using `properties` element instead of `properties.generic` and switching from `jakartaee-10.0` to `webProfile-10.0` + `enterpriseBeansLite-4.0`\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":444,"cache_read_input_tokens":133898,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":444,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1380},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3bf9647-5068-4947-ac84-3cc2f665ec1a","uuid":"2ca00de6-c776-457d-9362-da57c9315a69"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1189615,"duration_api_ms":945366,"num_turns":106,"result":"All tasks completed. Here is the migration report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks involved:** Quarkus 3.30.5 -> Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty)\n- **High-level actions performed:**\n  1. Analyzed 16 Java source files across entity, repository, service, and web layers\n  2. Replaced Quarkus BOM and all `io.quarkus` dependencies with `jakarta.jakartaee-api:10.0.0`\n  3. Migrated package names from `quarkus.tutorial.order` to `jakarta.tutorial.order`\n  4. Replaced Quarkus Qute templating with JAX-RS HTML string builders\n  5. Replaced Quarkus `@Observes StartupEvent` with Jakarta EE `@Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct`\n  6. Created Open Liberty server.xml, JPA persistence.xml, web.xml, and beans.xml\n  7. Updated Dockerfile to multi-stage build with Open Liberty runtime\n  8. Generated 6 smoke tests covering all major endpoints\n- **Overall outcome:** SUCCESS - All 6 smoke tests pass, application fully functional\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus dependencies with Jakarta EE 10 + Open Liberty\n- Dockerfile: Multi-stage build with Maven builder and Open Liberty runtime\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty server config (webProfile-10.0, H2 datasource)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit configuration\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Jakarta EE web application descriptor\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI 4.0 configuration\n- src/main/webapp/index.html: Redirect page to /orders\n- src/main/webapp/css/default.css: Stylesheet (copied from resources)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/entity/*.java: 7 entity classes (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/repository/*.java: 5 repository classes (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/service/OrderConfigService.java: Data init service (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderController.java: Business controller (package renamed)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderWebController.java: REST controller (Qute -> HTML builders)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/StartupInitializer.java: Startup EJB (StartupEvent -> @Singleton @Startup)\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/JakartaRestApplication.java: JAX-RS application class\n- smoke.py: 6 HTTP smoke tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/: Entire old package directory\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Quarkus-specific configuration\n- src/main/resources/templates/: Qute templates (orders.html, orderTemplate.html, lineItems.html, lineItemTemplate.html)\n- src/main/resources/css/: CSS (moved to webapp)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T03:30:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - 16 Java files, Quarkus 3.30.5\n[2026-03-17T03:31:00Z] [info] Generated smoke.py with 6 test cases\n[2026-03-17T03:32:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml - replaced all Quarkus deps with Jakarta EE 10\n[2026-03-17T03:33:00Z] [info] Created server.xml, persistence.xml, web.xml, beans.xml\n[2026-03-17T03:34:00Z] [info] Migrated all Java packages quarkus.tutorial -> jakarta.tutorial\n[2026-03-17T03:36:00Z] [info] Replaced Quarkus StartupEvent with @Singleton @Startup @PostConstruct\n[2026-03-17T03:36:30Z] [info] Replaced Qute templates with HTML string builders\n[2026-03-17T03:38:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile - multi-stage build with Open Liberty\n[2026-03-17T03:39:00Z] [error] Build fail: apt-get not found on UBI image - fixed to dnf\n[2026-03-17T03:40:00Z] [error] H2 URL format error + ORB error - fixed server.xml config\n[2026-03-17T03:41:00Z] [info] Successful build and deployment - Liberty started in 3.9s\n[2026-03-17T03:42:00Z] [info] All 6 smoke tests passed (0 failures)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 2 errors encountered and resolved during Doc